This is Perl module App::CLI::Plugin::Log::Message.

INSTALLATION

App::CLI::Plugin::Log::Message installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan App::CLI::Plugin::Log::Message

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

App::CLI::Plugin::Log::Message documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc App::CLI::Plugin::Log::Message

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

